data.description: Welcome to 609 Wharton St., This 3-story home sits next to Gold Star Park, a well-kept small community park. 609 Wharton St. is a very well-kept home with strong bones. Entering the home, you are greeted with a spacious wide open living & dining space. The kitchen space includes a less formal eating area and leads out to the backyard with plenty of potential. The 2nd floor includes 2 bedrooms and a large full bath, with a big closet in the bathroom for storage. The 3rd floor is currently an open space used as the 3rd bedroom.  This home has endless possibilities and has always been well kept.
